<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>{{ inventory_hostname | upper }} — Ansible</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
{% if server_color == 'blue' %}
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027 0%, #203a43 50%, #2c5364 100%);
{% else %}
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0533 0%, #2d1b69 50%, #11998e 100%);
{% endif %}
      color: white;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 50px 60px;
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 92%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    .server-badge {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
{% if server_color == 'blue' %}
      color: #4fc3f7;
{% else %}
      color: #ce93d8;
{% endif %}
    }
    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 5px 18px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
{% if server_color == 'blue' %}
      background: rgba(79,195,247,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(79,195,247,0.4);
      color: #4fc3f7;
{% else %}
      background: rgba(206,147,216,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(206,147,216,0.4);
      color: #ce93d8;
{% endif %}
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .desc {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
    }
    .box .lbl {
      font-size: 9px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .box .val {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
    }
    .rolling-banner {
      background: rgba(255,193,7,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,193,7,0.3);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #ffd54f;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .status {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3);
      color: #4ade80;
      padding: 10px 26px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .dot {
      width: 7px; height: 7px;
      background: #4ade80;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%,100% { opacity:1; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity:0.4; transform: scale(0.8); }
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 26px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">

    <div class="server-badge">{{ inventory_hostname | upper }}</div>
    <div class="tag">🚀 Rolling Deployment — Ansible</div>

    <h1>{{ server_description }}</h1>
    <p class="desc">
      Déployé automatiquement par <strong>Ansible</strong><br/>
      Stratégie : <strong>Rolling Deployment</strong> (serial: 1)<br/>
      Serveur web : <strong>Apache2</strong> sur Ubuntu
    </p>

    <div class="rolling-banner">
      🔁 Rolling Deployment actif — les serveurs sont mis à jour<br/>
      <strong>un par un</strong> pour garantir zéro interruption de service
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="box">
        <div class="lbl">Hostname</div>
        <div class="val">{{ inventory_hostname }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <div class="lbl">IP Interne</div>
        <div class="val">{{ ansible_host }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <div class="lbl">IP Publique</div>
        <div class="val">{{ server_ip_public }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <div class="lbl">Outil</div>
        <div class="val">Ansible</div>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <div class="lbl">Serveur Web</div>
        <div class="val">Apache2</div>
      </div>
      <div class="box">
        <div class="lbl">OS</div>
        <div class="val">Ubuntu</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="status">
      <div class="dot"></div>
      Serveur opérationnel
    </div>

    <footer>{{ projet_nom }}</footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
